      <ownedComment xmi:id="eabcaf1d-b71d-41da-b9c7-f16b1d613ebc" body="A boundary is a class that lies on the periphery of a system, but within it. It interacts with actors outside the system as well as with entity, control, and other boundary classes within the system." annotatedElement="bfb8dd01-3b9e-430c-b147-943a74f2083c">
